data.description: NEW ROOF! NEW SIDING ! NEW PRICE!  Want to be Home for the Holidays? Stunning 3+-Bedroom Home with Upgrades Galore! Welcome to your dream home! This beautifully renovated 3-bedroom, 2 and a half bath residence is now on the market, and it's ready to exceed your expectations. Nestled in a charming neighborhood, this property boasts a range of impressive features that make it a standout choice for your next home. New Roof: Say goodbye to worries about leaks or repairs. This home comes with a brand-new roof, ensuring durability and peace of mind for years to come. You can rest easy, knowing that the top of your new home is as pristine as the inside. New Siding: The exterior of this residence has been completely revitalized with new siding. Not only does this enhance the curb appeal, but it also adds an extra layer of insulation, making your home more energy-efficient. The sleek and modern design will make your property stand out in the neighborhood. Irresistible New Price: We understand the importance of finding a home that aligns with your budget. That's why we are thrilled to announce a new, competitive price for this fantastic property. Don't miss out on the chance to own a recently renovated home at an incredible value. 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths: The interior of the house is designed for comfort and convenience. With three spacious bedrooms and two and a half baths, this home offers ample space for families of all sizes. The primary bedroom includes an ensuite bath, providing a private retreat within your own home.  Versatile Additional Room: One of the standout features of this property is the extra room that awaits your creative touch. Whether you envision it as a spacious 4th bedroom, a quiet den for relaxation, or a productive home office, this bonus space adds unmatched flexibility to the floor plan.  Cozy Den Retreat: Embrace the warmth and charm of this versatile space as a den. With its inviting ambiance and proximity to the heart of the home, it's an ideal spot for unwinding after a long day, reading a good book, or enjoying quality time with loved ones.  Functional Home Office: If working from home is part of your routine, transform the room into a dedicated home office. The natural light filtering through the windows creates an inspiring atmosphere, making it the perfect setting for increased productivity. This additional room opens the door to a world of possibilities, allowing you to customize your home to fit your unique lifestyle. Whether you're expanding your family, creating a space for relaxation, or establishing a productive work environment, this home effortlessly adapts to your needs.  Hardwood Floors: Step inside, and you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting ambiance created by the gleaming hardwood floors. Not only do they add a touch of elegance, but they're also easy to maintain, ensuring a beautiful and durable flooring solution.  Partially Finished Basement: Need extra space for a home office, gym, or entertainment room? The partially finished basement is a versatile space that can be customized to suit your lifestyle. The additional square footage adds significant value to this already impressive home.  This home truly offers the perfect blend of modern upgrades and classic charm. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or looking to upgrade to a more spacious residence, this property is a must-see. Don't miss out on the chance to own a property that not only meets your current requirements but also grows with you in the years to come. Schedule a viewing and explore the potential of this remarkable home – where every room tells a story, and the next chapter is yours to write.
